{"tid":2267222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不做中共的小白鼠！巴西聖保羅民眾群起抗議中國疫苗","createTime":"2020-11-02T02:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:07:00.000Z","uid":337052,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"67a1e43f392b88776d83e42fdc63ab4eafeae797","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:25:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">不做中共的小白鼠！巴西聖保羅民眾群起抗議中國疫苗</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/02/phpny57An.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F02%2Fphpny57An.jpg&h=9c3e5688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西聖保羅州引進中國的武漢肺炎疫苗並展開第3階段的臨床試驗，當地民眾憤怒地走上街頭抗議。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2020/11/02 10:12<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">巴西聖保羅州引進中國科興生物的武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫苗，展開第3階段的臨床試驗，但聖保羅民眾憤怒地走上街頭抗議，高呼他們不願意當中國的小白鼠。</span><br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，巴西許多疫苗都是強制施打的，例如新生兒的B肝疫苗，以及1980年代全國性的小兒麻痺疫苗。在這樣的狀況下，聖保羅州長多利亞（Jo&atilde;o Doria）支持強制性武漢肺炎疫苗接種，並在州內進行中國疫苗的臨床試驗。<br />\n<br />\n巴西衛生部上個月更宣布，在多利亞的支持下未來將購買4600萬劑科興生物的疫苗。不過，巴西總統波索納洛（Jair Bolsonaro）立即出面阻止，因為他認為注射疫苗必須是自願性的。<span class=\"red\">巴西最高法院則表示，若疫苗通過實驗將由大法官裁決是否強制全國施打。<br />\n</span><br />\n事實上，從2018年參選總統開始，波索納洛就不斷地抨擊中國，聖保羅州的民眾也紛紛上街遊行支持總統，他們高舉的標語上寫著「我們不是小白鼠」、「不要疫苗」。<br />\n<br />\n抗議民眾佩特羅斯（Andre Petros）直呼<span class=\"red\">「我們反對專制的中國使者多利亞，他的強制性疫苗違反了我們的意願，這種事情在世界任何地方都不會發生，甚至在中國也不會發生。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/list/breakingnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Flist%2Fbreakingnews&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=e9046d37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Flist%2Fbreakingnews&h=07b1c327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/list/breakingnews</a>"},{"pid":"cd85a5248dc3f584b85b6d1f978a9b569de97708","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/02/phpny57An.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F02%2Fphpny57An.jpg&h=9c3e5688&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e91678bf51fb391c107229c7d015c78c172aa99","tid":2267222,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505aa29f91fae2fefc042e2a3657bca410a235c9","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ssicca1/status/1323039716242018305?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fssicca1%2Fstatus%2F1323039716242018305%3Fs%3D20&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=a9029cfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fssicca1%2Fstatus%2F1323039716242018305%3Fs%3D20&h=c66d05cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ssicca1/status/1323039716242018305?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DouglasGarcia/status/1323007946029174791?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDouglasGarcia%2Fstatus%2F1323007946029174791%3Fs%3D20&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=8ae8307c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDouglasGarcia%2Fstatus%2F1323007946029174791%3Fs%3D20&h=dca7d003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DouglasGarcia/status/1323007946029174791?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"190b7e2cd0545751d26678fa0e0849a5d19de1e9","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e91678bf51fb391c107229c7d015c78c172aa99","tid":2267222,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff023aa4e707c2d859a3006c9807d2ff7cfd2ce","tid":2267222,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"190b7e2cd0545751d26678fa0e0849a5d19de1e9","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e91678bf51fb391c107229c7d015c78c172aa99","tid":2267222,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9831c10a7cd13dd4f02000376c35a663bf2da72","tid":2267222,"uid":303038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:27:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"783e41a36469a8848c2dbc5f891e98aa4324a4a9","tid":2267222,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e2111aa4486d93c41a75eb967d8966ac919306","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>巴西民眾拒當中國疫苗白老鼠 示威反對強制接種</strong></span><br />\n最新更新：2020/11/02 09:35<br />\n<br />\n（中央社聖保羅1日綜合外電報導）巴西逾300名民眾今天聚集在聖保羅主要商業街，抗議州長多利亞支持強制接種2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫苗，以及接受中國科興生物公司研發的潛在疫苗測試。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，多利亞（Joao Doria）曾表達贊成疫苗出爐後便強制民眾接種，與誓言讓民眾自願接種的總統波索納洛（Jair Bolsonaro）起紛爭。最高法院首席大法官已表示此事將由法院做出最終定奪。<br />\n<br />\n巴西有一些強制施打的疫苗，包括提供新生兒接種的B型肝炎疫苗。巴西過去曾有過相當成功的大規模疫苗活動，比如在1980年代根除小兒麻痺症。<br />\n<br />\n在多利亞政府支持下，中國科興生物2019冠狀病毒疾病疫苗正在聖保羅（Sao Paulo）進行第3階段臨床試驗。<br />\n<br />\n巴西衛生部上個月宣布，待主管機構批准後，將採購4600萬劑疫苗，這項交易獲得各州州長支持。但右翼的波索納洛隔天便推翻這項決定，表示巴西不會採購這款疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n波索納洛從2018年競選期間迄今，斷斷續續就亞洲國家增加在巴西的投資和影響力一事抨擊中國。<br />\n<br />\n聖保羅抗議民眾今天集會支持波索納洛，其中一名示威者手持標語，上面寫著「我們不是白老鼠」，另一名戴著口罩的民眾手中標語寫著「不要疫苗」。擁擠的抗議人群中，許多人沒有配戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n抗議民眾佩特羅斯（Andre Petros）表示：「我們反對獨裁的中國大使多利亞，他現在要違反我們的意願讓疫苗變為強制性。」<br />\n<br />\n「世界上沒有任何地方會發生這種事，即使是在中國。」<br />\n<br />\n據路透社統計，巴西目前約有550萬起確診病例，是全球染疫人數第3多的國家，僅次於美國和印度。（譯者：李佩珊/核稿：盧映孜）1091102<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011020015.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202011020015.aspx&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=e45d3280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011020015.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"3a8fcfcff14dc8cf15e5ea1aa963e37ae03c1df1","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"783e41a36469a8848c2dbc5f891e98aa4324a4a9","tid":2267222,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f48f48e11ae33155b8eeeaaf2a403a001c6e38","tid":2267222,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"氣炸級嘴炮準備！3！2！1！發射！"},{"pid":"d3a9a63a0e394604d2ac1de49ed95499e8794595","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ElxFdqAXIAYp4Gl?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FElxFdqAXIAYp4Gl%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=c0f3ccbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55fef035b5676e8ea34e77fc7394260e07cef304","tid":2267222,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eee42cd673e24b3762d7f831e368b89f44c2fe","tid":2267222,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"巴西未富先驕"},{"pid":"7122985d8e1ed78a03d8b9a6fa05ea36ceb6e7b1","tid":2267222,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"其實巴西係咪垃圾國家嚟<br />\n巴西總統中咗中國肺炎 仆過一次街都仲未驚 <br />\n仲想仆第二次？仲要用中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf8ff20490914d3c4d9832674b7c349091c3d7b","tid":2267222,"uid":56957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"隻疫苗對1 percent人有負作用 後遺症什至死<br />\n分分鐘仲慘過中武肺<br />\n強制幾百幾千萬人試隻新疫苗 有幾多油水係到呢"},{"pid":"52fe73332e09080ece98cf819d7628054cb79c5a","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ElxhSW4WkAMak39?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FElxhSW4WkAMak39%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=a2507586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"199267f509f0e8ace960d6b1a729bcf0a1fdd406","tid":2267222,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"Milk Tea Alliance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cd68889d4534e95498e24ae835923989040101","tid":2267222,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9ae1f67782cc86e887da5e2889286eb78fee59","tid":2267222,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"199267f509f0e8ace960d6b1